[35m│[0m  [92mREVIEW INSTRUCTIONS:[0m                                                                                                                                                                   [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Examine the calculation method chosen by the expert[0m                                                                                                                                  [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Verify each mathematical operation is performed correctly[0m                                                                                                                            [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Check if the calculation sequence is logical and appropriate[0m                                                                                                                         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Assess if the final result makes business/financial sense[0m                                                                                                                            [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Ensure proper handling of percentages, ratios, and financial scales[0m                                                                                                                  [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92mCommon calculation patterns to verify:[0m                                                                                                                                                 [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Percentage change: (new - old) / old × 100%[0m                                                                                                                                          [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Growth rates: (current - previous) / previous[0m                                                                                                                                        [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Ratios: numerator / denominator[0m                                                                                                                                                      [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- Differences: value1 - value2[0m                                                                                                                                                         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92mProvide your assessment in this format:[0m                                                                                                                                                [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- APPROVED: If calculation logic is sound and correct[0m                                                                                                                                  [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m  [92m- NEEDS_IMPROVEMENT: If there are mathematical or logical issues[0m                                                                                                                       [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                         [35m│[0m
